Install MIT Scheme on MacOS: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12322434/how-to-install-mit-scheme-on-mac
Scheme's sourcecode extension: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36240629/whats-the-proper-scheme-file-extension
Execute Scheme scripts outside repl: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/903968/how-do-i-execute-a-scm-script-outside-of-the-repl-with-mit-scheme

Then just type `scheme` in terminal enter repl mode, or type `scheme < schemeScript.scm` to test code.